flowchart LR
  BW[Billable Work - upstream context]
  DL[Invoice Drafts List - worklist]
  DB[Draft Builder - compose or edit]
  RD[Readiness gate - Ready or Not Ready]
  IS[Issue - semantic boundary]
  II[Issued Invoice - document truth snapshot]
  HO[Handoff to Receivables - downstream context link]

  BW --> DL --> DB --> RD
  RD -->|Not Ready| DB
  RD -->|Ready| IS --> II --> HO

  subgraph Boundary[Boundary rules]
    BR1[Post issue draft changes do not rewrite issued snapshot]
    BR2[No Paid or Overdue statuses inside Invoice document status]
  end

  II -.-> BR1
  DL -.-> BR2
